---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Sincloy Games"
	description="Learn about our mission to create innovative gaming experiences"
	pubDate={new Date('March 15 2025')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Sincloy Games is an independent game development studio founded by passionate creators dedicated to pushing the boundaries of interactive entertainment. We believe in the power of games to tell compelling stories and create unforgettable experiences.
	</p>

	<p>
		Our team brings together diverse talents from across the gaming industry, united by a shared vision of creating games that inspire, challenge, and entertain. While we're currently in the early stages of development, we're working hard to bring our first projects to life.
	</p>

	<p>
		At Sincloy Games, we value:
		<ul>
			<li>Innovation in gameplay mechanics</li>
			<li>Immersive storytelling</li>
			<li>Artistic expression</li>
			<li>Player engagement</li>
			<li>Community involvement</li>
		</ul>
	</p>

	<p>
		We're committed to creating games that not only entertain but also challenge players to think differently. Our development philosophy emphasizes quality over quantity, and we're dedicated to crafting experiences that resonate with players on a deeper level.
	</p>

	<p>
		Stay tuned as we continue our journey in game development. We can't wait to share our creations with the world and become part of your gaming experiences.
	</p>
</Layout>
